title: It's Going To Happen Quickly | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: It's Going To Happen Quickly | Joel Osteen
description:
There are some moments God has prepared to do a quick work in your life. The obstacle you’re facing may look permanent, but in a moment, God can turn it around. You’re about to step into a sudden breakthrough!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
